divs: Sighting DetailsWe witnessed a hovering light west of the city. Remained in Sky for over 5 hours, hovering. Flashed Red-Blue-Green, with white flashes. Also red plusing lights top and bottom, alternating with flashing. Lights appeared to move on a liner plane as if the object was disc-shaped.
